          <p class="footer__desc">Fabrikanizi tek bir akilli platformdan yonetin. Siskon Otomasyon'un uretim yonetim cozumu.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer__col">
          <h6 class="footer__heading">Platform</h6>
          <ul class="footer__links">
            <li><a href="#">Genel Bakis</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">OEE & Performans</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Dashboard</a></li>
            <li><a href="#">Entegrasyon</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        <div class="footer__col">
